  "title": "6723 - Technical Sales Consultant (BIM Software) – Construction Technology | $3,500–$5,000 + Commission + Mobile/Transport Allowance | Requires ability to demo BIM tools + full sales cycle",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Sales Consultant (Digital Software – BIM / Digital Construction)</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Salary Range:</strong> SGD <strong>$3,500 – $5,000</strong> + Commission + Monthly Mobile/Transport Allowance<br>\n<strong>Location:</strong>  (Redhill MRT)<br>\n<strong>Working Days:</strong> Monday – Friday<br>\n<strong>Working Hours:</strong> 9am – 6pm</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Identify client requirements in the AEC sector and recommend suitable BIM or digital construction solutions.</li>\n  <li>Conduct product demonstrations, presentations, and prepare proposals or quotations.</li>\n  <li>Develop new business opportunities and manage customer accounts.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with internal technical teams to support project delivery and ensure fulfilment of customer requirements.</li>\n  <li>Manage sales pipeline activities and prepare sales reports.</li>\n  <li>Monitor BIM-related market trends, competitor products, and industry developments.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirements / Qualifications</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or Degree in Engineering, Architecture, Construction Management, Business, or related fields.</li>\n  <li>Minimum <strong>2–3 years of sales experience</strong> in construction technology, software, or relevant industries.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of BIM platforms such as Autodesk Revit, Navisworks, Synchro, Bentley, or similar software will be an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Ability to conduct product demonstrations and presentations on BIM or digital construction solutions.</li>\n  <li>Ability to manage sales processes including prospecting, proposal preparation, and follow-up.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wa.me/6596420989\"><strong>https://wa.me/6596420989</strong></a></p>\n<p><strong>WhatsApp: +65 9642 0989   (Han)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Email: </strong><a href=\"mailto:supreme.cc.han@gmail.com\"><strong>supreme.cc.han@gmail.com</strong></a></p>\n<p><strong>Chaw Chiaw Han, Reg No:   R22106723</strong></p>\n<p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte   Ltd, EA No: 14c7279</strong></p>",
